data.description: *SEE PRIVATE REMARKS FOR AVAILABLE FINANCE OPTIONS** Newly remodeled 4-bedroom home! Engineer Certification completed. Horse property in beautiful Rainbow Valley. This move in ready home offers vaulted ceilings, skylights, wood flooring and a beautiful, stacked stone fireplace. Open kitchen floor plan with beautiful breakfast/dining room.  Kitchen features new range and microwave all white appliances, new cabinets and counter tops with plenty of counter space. Spacious main suite bathroom with dual sink vanity and two walk in closets, garden tub, separate shower.  Extended covered porch in the front and the back which overlook the vast acreage and majestic mountains. Bring your horses and your toys! New septic system installed. All electric and plumbing is updated. Washer/Dryer included
